OL,3,CBarclays net zero goals questioned as
OL,4,Chelped fund $1.7 billion for US coal
OL,5,Cpower
OL,7,FBy ITV News Business and Economics
OL,8,FProducer Mahatir Pasha and The Bureau
OL,9,Fof Investigative Journalism's
OL,10,FJosephine Moulds
OL,12,FOn the banks of the Ohio River in the
OL,13,FUnited States, you'll find the Ghent
OL,14,Fpower plant.
OL,16,FIt generates electricity using coal,
OL,17,Fthe world's most polluting fossil fuel.
