OL,3,CBarclays net zero goals questioned as
OL,4,Chelped fund $1.7 billion for US coal
OL,5,Cpower
OL,7,FEvery year, Kentucky Utilities burns
OL,8,Ffive and half million tonnes of coal
OL,9,Fat this site, enough to power half a
OL,10,Fmillion homes.
OL,12,FThe US coal industry has been in
OL,13,Fdramatic decline in recent years,
OL,14,Funder pressure from renewable power
OL,15,Fand an abundance of cheaper shale gas.
OL,17,FBut coal is not dead yet and Barclays
OL,18,FBank is one of the banks helping to
OL,19,Fkeep it alive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
