OL,3,CBarclays net zero goals questioned as
OL,4,Chelped fund $1.7 billion for US coal
OL,5,Cpower
OL,7,FBarclays has an ambition to reach Net
OL,8,FZero by 2050.
OL,10,FTo get there, the bank is not required
OL,11,Fto immediately stop doing business
OL,12,Fwith companies which use coal, but it
OL,13,Fdoes need to phase out such lending.
OL,15,FBarclays Climate Change Statement,
OL,16,Fpublished in February 2024, sets out
OL,17,Fthe bank's policies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
