OL,3,CBarclays net zero goals questioned as
OL,4,Chelped fund $1.7 billion for US coal
OL,5,Cpower
OL,7,FThe document states Barclays will not
OL,8,Fprovide "any financing to clients that
OL,9,Fgenerate more than 50% of revenues
OL,10,Ffrom thermal coal-fired power
OL,11,Fgeneration".
OL,13,FThe pledge was first made four years
OL,14,Fago but it doesn't go as far as the
OL,15,Fpledges made by the UK's other big
OL,16,Fbanks - HSBC, NatWest and Lloyds.
OL,18,FAnd some argue that, in practice, this
OL,19,Fpledge is largely meaningless.
