OL,5,Cpower
OL,7,FTwo loans of $400 million were for
OL,8,FMonongahela Power which got all of its
OL,9,Frevenues from selling electricity -
OL,10,F95% of which came from burning coal at
OL,11,Ftwo power stations in West Virginia.
OL,13,FIn addition to the Monongahela deals,
OL,14,FBarclays helped raise $400 million for
OL,15,FKentucky Utilities, which appeared to
OL,16,Fget 73% of the electricity it sold in
OL,17,F2022 from burning coal.
