OL,4,Chelped fund $1.7 billion for US coal
OL,5,Cpower
OL,7,FBarclays also helped raise a $500
OL,8,Fmillion loan for Louisville Gas &
OL,9,FElectric. The company makes some of
OL,10,Fits revenues from selling gas but
OL,11,Fcalculations based on company and
OL,12,Fgovernment data suggest its revenue
OL,13,Fshare from coal, was 57%.
OL,15,FNone of these companies plans to stop
OL,16,Fusing coal by 2030, a deadline climate
OL,17,Fscientists say is critical.
OL,19,FBarclays says it hasn't breached its
OL,20,Fcoal policy which it insists is robust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
