OL,7,FBarclays declined ITV News' request
OL,8,Ffor an interview.
OL,10,FOn Thursday, the bank held a results
OL,11,Fcall for journalists.
OL,13,FOrdinarily, we are able to ask a
OL,14,Fquestion to its chief executive but
